title: 102. …But Helth? Ft. Dr. Russell Surasky
itunes:title: 102. …But Helth? Ft. Dr. Russell Surasky
description: Has this Coronavirus pandemic been about health? Or has it been about money? On today’s episode, Andy and the crew are joined by Dr. Russell Surasky, the only triple board-certified neurologist in the United States as they discuss the science behind the COVID-19 vaccine, mask inefficiencies, and the role mainstream media and politicians have played in this pandemic.
